browser-description =
    FreeSynergy Browser is the integrated web browser for the FreeSynergy desktop.

    It is designed to display service UIs, the Store, and admin panels with
    automatic IAM token injection from Kanidm — users never need to log in
    separately to each service.

    In terminal environments it provides a TUI mode for server administration
    without a graphical display.

browser-features =
    - Automatic IAM token injection (seamless SSO)
    - Tab support
    - S3 download integration
    - TUI mode for server/terminal environments
    - Embedded in the FreeSynergy Desktop
